OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FP&O forced to reverse      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fattempt at pay cut         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ferry company P&O has been forced to   
OL,6, reverse an attempt to pay its new,     
OL,7, cheaper seafarers less money.          
OL,9,FIt comes after the RMT Union received  
OL,10,Freports of agency workers at Dover     
OL,11,Fbeing asked to sign contracts replacing
OL,12,Ftheir old ones with reduced payment.   
OL,14,FThe union reported P&O to the Maritime 
OL,15,Fand Coastguard Agency, which ensured   
OL,16,Fthe new workers retained their original
OL,17,Fwages.                                 
OL,19,FThe ferry company has been asked for   
OL,20,Fcomment but has so far not responded.  
